snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedVariables

client = AsyncSeedVariables(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.service.post(
        endpoint_param="endpointParam",
    )


asyncio.run(main())
